      {
        "path": "README.md",
        "language": "markdown",
        "preview": "# Please Create An Implementation Plan For\n\nGenerated by Binary IDE as a portable `package_bundle` starter bundle.\n\n## Intent\n\nplease create an implementation plan for a new take profit level\n\n## Run\n\n```bash\nnpm install\nnpm run build\nnpm start\n```\n\n## Runtime\n\n- Runtime: node18\n- Platform: portable\n- Package manager: npm\n",
        "hash": "d42b85936460404f9f0a6b5b9cd38dc4e8d33372eb221500d339253339ec3e94",
